            <div class="title">
                Clause 13—(Charge Of Income Tax For 1951–52)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-06-06/debates/f710b817-18c4-4e20-a82d-014a9fa31175/AgedSick" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
