        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a9eca1ad-b2e6-47f3-9a78-ae15b591ed01">
                Mr. H. Hynd  (Accrington)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a9eca1ad-b2e6-47f3-9a78-ae15b591ed01" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-06/debates/ac13770b-e217-4de7-ad7c-c6648ece3e57/Clause13%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1951%E2%80%9352)#contribution-a9eca1ad-b2e6-47f3-9a78-ae15b591ed01">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Did not the hon. Member, at Question time the other day, complain about excessive profits now being paid out and ask that they be restricted?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a9eca1ad-b2e6-47f3-9a78-ae15b591ed01" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-06/debates/ac13770b-e217-4de7-ad7c-c6648ece3e57/Clause13%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1951%E2%80%9352)#contribution-a9eca1ad-b2e6-47f3-9a78-ae15b591ed01">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
