                The Chancellor of the Exchequer (Mr. Gaitskell)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3fde6f14-9e2e-40b5-8c6d-44d01be2edc4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
