                Mr. Gaitskell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b9e79860-6e65-45b5-9101-a14f6113e32c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-06/debates/ac13770b-e217-4de7-ad7c-c6648ece3e57/Clause13%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1951%E2%80%9352)#contribution-b9e79860-6e65-45b5-9101-a14f6113e32c">
